    "headline": "Wolfspeed Appoints Semiconductor Industry Veteran Yasuhisa Harita",
    "summary": "DURHAM, N.C., April 22, 2026--Wolfspeed, Inc. announced today the appointment of Yasuhisa Harita as regional president for Asia Pacific effective June 1, 2026. Harita will be based in Tokyo and lead Wolfspeed’s commercial strategy across Japan, Korea and the ASEAN region with responsibility for driving revenue growth, enhancing strategic customer relationships, and executing the company’s regional commercial and operational objectives.",
